    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and requires significant attention. It currently has major mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that is starting to slip. Cosmetically, the exterior has several dents and fading paint, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This car is recommended for someone looking for a major project or for parts, and it is sold strictly as-is.",
