    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone prioritizing function over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission remain reliable, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some minor staining on the carpet. It has been recently serviced to ensure it is road-ready, though a new owner might want to address the cosmetic issues over time.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterclass in automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in true showroom condition, having been curated with an uncompromising attention to detail that is evident in every stitch and surface. From its mirror-finish exterior to its pristine, smoke-free cabin, this car transcends the typical pre-owned experience. It has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical and aesthetic excellence. For the discerning collector or driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride of a lifetime. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and kept in what I can only describe as showroom-fresh condition. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly looks even better in person. There might be a tiny, microscopic mark if you really go looking for it, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as you'll ever find. Come by for a coffee and a look; I'd love to see her go to a good home!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine, museum-grade E46 M3 that defines the 'ultimate driving machine.' This S54 powerplant is a mechanical masterpiece, delivering surgical throttle response and high-RPM harmonic stability that modern turbocharged engines simply cannot replicate. I have proactively addressed the chassis' Achilles heels: the subframe has been structurally reinforced with plate kits exceeding factory rigidity, and the VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed with upgraded solenoids and seals. Compression and leak-down tests show factory-spec tolerances across all six cylinders. The suspension geometry is perfected with fresh bushings and high-damping Bilstein units, ensuring zero deflection and laser-accurate turn-in. This is a turn-key, high-fidelity driver\u2019s car with a service history that reflects zero compromises on component integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Better than new. First to see will buy. Won't last.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history. This shimmering sapphire coupe isn't just a car; it's a preserved moment in time, a relic of an era where every curve was sculpted by hand and every mile told a story. The leather interior carries the faint, nostalgic scent of a private library, and the engine hums with the steady, rhythmic heartbeat of a champion resting between races. To drive it is to command the wind itself, turning every mundane commute into a cinematic escape. This is more than a vehicle; it\u2019s a soul-stirring companion waiting for its next great chapter. A true time capsule for the discerning soul.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This collector-grade specimen has been meticulously preserved, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for excellence. For the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best, this vehicle offers a level of refinement and integrity that is increasingly difficult to source. Experience the peace of mind that comes with a vehicle maintained to the highest possible standard.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    }
